responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "12B7E56E4D240BC2D7A9128E6B53F8B1", "I will certainly veil these quite well. No doubt the Athenaeum and the Academy are seeking them out as I scribe. Yet, I do have an artifact that can be put to use on the dimwitted species of this realm. It is a crude crown with the stench of rotting frogs. It is called the Crown of Mungle. Records state that it was formed on the eternal stench of the Mungle, a mythical swamp.")
name: MIDD_0020_MOM_Book_WizardJournal_6
